{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyPlCkeXSmLYhH/RMlf3hXfs"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"nCXr60D4A3Rg"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"221a1637"},"source":["## Notebook Summary\n","\n","**Objective:** The primary objective of this notebook was to load, clean, and prepare shipment data from the Apapa Port, and then to engineer new features for potential analysis.\n","\n","**Key Findings & Initial Issues:**\n","*   The dataset contained 5000 entries with 7 columns, detailing shipment information like cargo type, container size, and various dates.\n","*   Initially, all date columns (`Vessel_Arrival`, `Customs_Clearance`, `Truck_Dispatch`) were of `object` (string) type, requiring conversion to datetime objects for calculations.\n","*   The `Truck_Dispatch` column had 250 missing values, all corresponding to shipments with a 'Pending Dispatch' status, which is a logical consistency.\n","*   A significant data quality issue was identified: 50 records had `Customs_Clearance` dates occurring *before* `Vessel_Arrival` dates, which is physically impossible.\n","*   One `Cargo_Type` entry (' Electronics') had a leading space, indicating a need for potential string cleaning, though this wasn't explicitly addressed in the provided cleaning steps.\n","\n","**Solutions & Steps Taken:**\n","*   **Data Type Conversion:** All relevant date columns (`Vessel_Arrival`, `Customs_Clearance`, `Truck_Dispatch`) were successfully converted to datetime objects using `pd.to_datetime` to enable date-based computations.\n","*   **Logical Inconsistency Correction:** For the 50 identified records where `Customs_Clearance` was earlier than `Vessel_Arrival`, the dates in these two columns were swapped to ensure logical consistency. A verification step confirmed that this issue was resolved.\n","*   **Feature Engineering:** Three new lead time features were created:\n","    *   `Clearance_Lead_Days`: Days between `Vessel_Arrival` and `Customs_Clearance`.\n","    *   `Dispatch_Lead_Days`: Days between `Customs_Clearance` and `Truck_Dispatch`.\n","    *   `Total_Lead_Days`: Total days from `Vessel_Arrival` to `Truck_Dispatch`.\n","\n","In essence, the notebook successfully performed essential data cleaning and feature engineering to prepare the raw shipment data for further analysis, addressing critical data quality issues."]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from google.colab import drive\n","drive.mount('/content/drive')"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"qm25Dfj5ocHQ","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1771959074563,"user_tz":-60,"elapsed":5244,"user":{"displayName":"Seyi Popoola","userId":"10254665942217023304"}},"outputId":"f22ec730-6acd-40f1-9f75-340f04d64711"},"execution_count":37,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Drive already mounted at /content/drive; to attempt to forcibly remount, call drive.mount(\"/content/drive\", force_remount=True).\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":38,"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":313},"id":"d5vqXI8Hn4-d","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1771959074662,"user_tz":-60,"elapsed":80,"user":{"displayName":"Seyi Popoola","userId":"10254665942217023304"}},"outputId":"1c88cbd9-714c-4d27-e31d-843dbd1c4d8e"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["    Shipment_ID        Cargo_Type Container_Size Vessel_Arrival  \\\n","0  SHP-AP-10000              FMCG           20ft     2025-04-06   \n","1  SHP-AP-10001  Medical Supplies           20ft     2025-02-05   \n","2  SHP-AP-10002     Raw Materials           40ft     2025-04-24   \n","3  SHP-AP-10003       Electronics           20ft     2025-02-06   \n","4  SHP-AP-10004              FMCG           40ft     2025-01-14   \n","